{
  "texts": [
    "Unlike other evaluation metrics such as BLEU [31] and CHRF [32], BERTScore takes into account the semantic context and can provide more accurate and consistent evaluations of generated or translated sentences.",
    "It is widely used in natural language processing research to assess the quality of language generation.",
    "• UNIEVAL: [33] UNIEVAL is an innovative and multidimensional evaluation system designed for text generation tasks.",
    "It utilizes a unified approach based on Boolean Question Answering to assess generated text from various perspectives using a single model.",
    "UNIEVAL evaluates sentences based on different linguistic qualities such as coherence, cohesion, fluency, and relevance."
  ]
}